Interface LoadableMod<L>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - base class type for Comparable so that implementors can specify their Comparable type
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<L>, Injectable, Loadable<L>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoadableMod.EmptyModContainer, LoadableModClassPath, LoadableModFile

    public interface LoadableMod<L>
extends Loadable<L>, Injectable
    Interface for containers which can be loaded as mods
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
